$ rule split_sentences
    (
        - sentence $( $words1 )+ . $( $words2 )+
    )
    (
        s $( $words1 )+ .
        s $( $words2 )+
    )

$ rule default_s
    (
        - s $( $words )+
    )
    (
        $ println (I didn't understand this sentence: ) $($words )+
    )

$ rule the_x_is_y
    (
        - s The $x is $y .
    )
    (
        $x is $y
    )

The hat is hard. This is the second sentence.

$ facts
$ assert hat is hard